data.description: This former model home has it all. This floor plan has 3 bedrooms PLUS a study at the front of the house. The 2 car garage has a storm shelter. The primary on suite has a separate shower and tub, large walk in closet and a towel warmer rack to keep you warm after your relaxing soak. The open concept kitchen has beautiful, dark quartz counter tops, stainless steel appliances and the LG fridge is included. Enjoy the luxury of a large flex space to use as a second dining room, playroom or craft area! Perfectly situated to back up to the disc golf course, walking trails, basketball court and playground! This house has too many upgrades to count! The study has upgraded plantation shutters, built-in overhead storage in the garage, a 5 zone sprinkler system and security system and cameras(Cox). Enjoy next to nothing electric bills thanks to the 6.3 KW Solar panels ($20K+ value). The back patio was meant for entertaining and comes with the outdoor TV, sound system, TV enclosure and even the small shed! LVP rigid core flooring in the main living spaces and the carpet in the bedrooms were all replaced in 2022. Water softener was installed in 2021 and the kitchen faucet has a reverse osmosis drinking spout. 50 Gallon water heater recently replaced and roof was replaced in August 2019!
